this_title: La Jeune fille et ses tocs
introduction: When Jo starts working at a new construction site, he hears a cello. It's Sophie's, or "Miss Crazy" as the boss of the café across the streets calls her. She tries to practise before the construction uproar takes over.Le matin où Jo intègre son chantier, il entend jouer du violoncelle. C’est Sophie, ou « Miss Dingo » comme l’appelle le patron du café d’en face. Elle s’entraine avant que le vacarme des machines commence…When Jo starts working at a new construction site, he hears a cello. It’s Sophie’s, or “Miss Crazy” as the boss of the café across the streets calls her. She tries to practise before the construction uproar takes over.
